room_title: Escape room "Wanted" by Locked 460 Escape Rooms in Grand Rapids
room_description: It’s 1883 and you and some other rustlers are visiting the local watering hole Locked & Loaded Saloon. Things were great until one of your sidekicks got out of hand. Apparently, they don’t like poker cheats in these parts. The barkeep locked up your buddy in jail! He has hidden your gun and left to go find the Sheriff to deal with your wild friend. You have 60 minutes to bust out your friend, find your gun and get out of Dodge before the Sheriff returns.
